Data Mask

Access Information About Specific Data Mask Job

The Run Logs tab in Data Mask is now the Jobs tab. From a list view in the Jobs tab, you can click the Data Mask name to view specific information about each mask.

Automate the Running of Data Mask Processes with Job Scheduler

Configure how frequently you run Data Mask, daily, weekly, or monthly, to mask all new data in your sandbox.

Other Improvements to Salesforce Data Mask

We’ve optimized the record loading and transformation so Data Mask jobs complete faster. When it completes a job, Data Mask now bypasses automation rather than deactivating or reactivating when a job is complete.
